# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in git.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if platform is not identical, the lock file should be ignored.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Using Poetry, it's common to ignore the virtualenv inside the project
